Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:02.41,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:120120,122415}The Crimson Goddess
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.66,0:02:06.79,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:121664,126794}Tsukikage Chigusa had firmly resolved\Nto stop at nothing to transform Kitajima Maya
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.79,0:02:10.54,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:126794,130548}into a world-class actress with a thousand masks,\Neven severing Maya's ties with her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.54,0:02:14.84,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:130548,134844}However, under a conspiracy\Norganized by Metropolitan Entertainment,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.84,0:02:16.72,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:134844,136720}Tsukikage Theatre's first play, "Little Women",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.72,0:02:20.14,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:136720,140141}received very harsh criticism,\Nand the theatre's future is uncertain.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.14,0:02:30.10,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:140141,150109}Tsukikage Theatre
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.26,0:02:27.14,Episode title,[title],0,0,0,,{TIME:141267,147148}{\an5\pos(766,710)\fscy95\blur1\fad(800,0)}—Episode 04—\NThe Lonely Battle
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.90,0:02:41.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157909,161412}How do you plan to handle\Nthese articles, Miss Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.78,0:02:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:162789,164332}We were set up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.33,0:02:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164332,166751}It doesn't matter if you were set up or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.75,0:02:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:166751,170755}It's pretty fair to say that your reputation\Nin the world of drama is ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.75,0:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:170755,174676}Miss Tsukikage, the reason our president\Ninvested in your theater was because
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.67,0:03:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174676,180556}he believed your actresses and stars\Nwould bring in lots of money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:180556,184727}With these kind of reviews,\Nnobody will cast your students.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.72,0:03:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:184727,188815}Where will the money come from\Nif you can't make any stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.81,0:03:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:188815,193027}What exactly would you like me to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.02,0:03:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193027,196280}I'm sure you have heard\Nabout this acting contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196280,200660}the Japanese Drama Associatiion\Nalways makes it into a big event.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.66,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:200660,202286}What do you think, Miss Tsukikage?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202286,207041}A first place win would be enough\Nto completely change your reputation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207041,210169}To keep Tsukikage Theatre\Nfrom going out of business,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:210169,212672}you have to do what needs to be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.00,0:03:36.75,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:214006,216758}Tsukikage Theatre… going out of business?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:47.43,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:223391,227436}National Acting Contest
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:229981,231774}Oh? Look over there!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.77,0:03:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231774,232275}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.90,0:03:57.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:233901,237780}Oh, they're the ones\Nthe tabloids mentioned…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.78,0:04:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:237780,241159}I think Aoyagi has been supporting them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.15,0:04:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241159,244120}I heard their first play was a total disaster.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.12,0:04:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:244120,246330}Yeah, they said it was embarrassingly amateur.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.79,0:04:10.79,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:248791,250793}{\fad(400,0)}Acting Contest Registration Form
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.41,0:04:11.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249417,251335}Please sign in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251335,253463}Tsukikage Theatre is registering, too…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.46,0:04:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:253463,255465}There's no place for beginners here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.46,0:04:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255465,258050}Bud I kind of want to see\Nhow badly they do.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.05,0:04:19.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258050,259093}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:21.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:260511,261888}So embarrassing…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.88,0:04:25.43,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:261888,265433}Those articles turned us\Nall into laughingstocks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.14,0:04:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:266142,267894}Why, if it isn't Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.93,0:04:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:269937,272273}Please wait outside, girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.27,0:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:272273,272939}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274609,278321}Tsukikage Theatre will be entering\Nthe contest too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.32,0:04:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:278321,280364}Anything wrong with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.36,0:04:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:280364,282158}Oh no, of course not.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.15,0:04:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282158,287371}Well, for your sake I hope\Nyou all do better this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:288748,292251}The potential of Tsukikage Theatre\Nhas obviously completely terrified you,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:292251,295671}otherwise you would not have employed\Nsuch an underhanded scheme.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.92,0:04:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296923,299592}You misunderstand.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.59,0:05:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299592,302970}Every single one of those articles was\Nthe untouched opinion of a professional critic.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.97,0:05:05.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:302970,305556}I will not be swayed by your corporate trickery.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.55,0:05:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:305556,306933}Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.93,0:05:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306933,309268}You should learn to respect criticism.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:309268,312480}You may not listen to them,,\Nbut the public will.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.48,0:05:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:312480,314482}Of course I sympathize with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.48,0:05:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:314482,318319}After all, Tsukikage Theatre is just starting out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.07,0:05:21.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:320071,321196}Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.19,0:05:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:321196,324574}If you gave Metropolitan Entertainment\Nthe play rights for "The Crimson Goddess",
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.57,0:05:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:324574,327119}all our lives would be much easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:327119,330373}Anyway, our business here is finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.13,0:05:44.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:343134,344470}What a terrible man!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.86,0:06:00.15,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:358860,360152}What a terrible man!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:05.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:364699,365491}Masumi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.30,0:06:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:383301,385552}Our drama guidelines for the pre-audition
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.55,0:06:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:385552,390057}of the National Acting Contest are as follows.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.05,0:06:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:390057,393311}The drama will be "Growing Up"\Nby Ichiyō Higuchi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.31,0:06:35.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:393311,395271}"Growing Up"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.27,0:06:36.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395271,396814}Yeah, you know,\Nthe one from the Meiji Era.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.81,0:06:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:396814,398691}Right, the story of Midori and Shinyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.69,0:06:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:398691,400026}Staged in Yoshiwara.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:400026,402445}Midori, the main role,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.44,0:06:44.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402445,404989}will be played by Kitajima Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:47.99,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:406699,407992}Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.82,0:06:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409827,411996}Shinyo is Morikawa Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.99,0:06:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:411996,413788}Wait a minute, Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.78,0:06:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413788,417168}There's no way I can play the main role\Nin such an important contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.16,0:06:58.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:417168,418961}Teacher…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:418961,421964}This is a crucial time for our theater.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.96,0:07:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:421964,425801}Besides, I only just started acting!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.80,0:07:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:425801,429847}Does anyone have any objections\Nto my casting decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.18,0:07:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432183,435186}Maya may be sort of inexperienced,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.18,0:07:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435186,438564}but her acting as Beth in "Little Women"\Nwas absolutely perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:438564,440024}I'd support her!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.02,0:07:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:440024,441150}You should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:441150,442652}You can do it, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.65,0:07:24.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:442652,444694}Go for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.57,0:07:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:452578,454497}I'm so happy…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.49,0:07:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:454497,457166}I always thought I was good for nothing…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.16,0:07:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:457166,460169}I truly believed that I really was…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.14,0:07:55.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:474141,475559}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.55,0:07:57.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:475559,477728}Tsukikage will direct\N"Growing Up", is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.72,0:07:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:477728,479355}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:479355,480271}I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.77,0:08:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483776,492617}According to the drama guidelines given to Ondine\Nfor the Tōkyō district pre-audition
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.61,0:08:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:492617,493494}we will perform "Growing Up".
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.41,0:08:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:494412,497748}The main role, Midori,\Nwill be played by Himekawa Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:22.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:499124,502211}Shinyo will be Sakurakōji Yū.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506841,508300}Sakurakōji.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.30,0:08:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:508300,511512}Let us work hard for the national contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.51,0:08:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:511512,512262}We sure will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:37.97,Sign,(sign),0,0,0,,{TIME:512765,517977}{\fad(1000,0)}"Growing Up"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:35.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:514765,515850}"Shinyo."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.85,0:08:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515850,517518}"Why don't you like me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.51,0:08:38.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:517518,518936}"Why are you so unfriendly to me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.93,0:08:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:518936,521439}"Why are you so cold to me?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.43,0:08:42.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:521439,522397}"Why?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:45.73,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:523941,525734}She appears competitive and saucy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.73,0:08:48.77,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:525734,528779}Yet she's feminine on the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.77,0:08:51.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:528779,531198}I can definitely relate to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.19,0:08:52.28,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531198,532282}It's easy!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.28,0:08:54.82,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532282,534827}I already know how to portray Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.82,0:08:56.41,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:534827,536412}Midori…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:09:00.20,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:536412,540207}I once had a classmate kind of like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.20,0:09:03.50,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540207,543502}She was beautiful and rich,\Nand everyone liked her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.50,0:09:07.84,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543502,547840}I've always dreamed of being\Nconfident and outspoken like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.84,0:09:12.47,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:547840,552470}Now I have the opportunity to do just that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.22,0:09:14.97,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:553220,554972}Acting is so much fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:18.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:554972,558225}I can use my acting\Nto become completely different people!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.60,0:09:22.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561604,562897}Please. please!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.89,0:09:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:562897,564440}Choose whatever you wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.44,0:09:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:564440,566400}I will take care of the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.23,0:09:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:568235,570654}Should we all get matching clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.65,0:09:35.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:570654,575159}Or should we visit Fude\Nto purchase our toys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:38.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:576994,578454}Teacher!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.08,0:09:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579080,582750}I just heard that Ondine\Nwill also be performing "Growing Up".
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.75,0:09:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:582750,583876}Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.33,0:09:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:586337,589465}Himekawa Ayumi is rumoured\Nto be in the lead role,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:51.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:589465,591550}and Shinyo will be played by Sakurakōji Yū.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.97,0:09:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:595971,597888}Thank you, we will now continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.47,0:10:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598474,601393}Now, come running from the right side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:04.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601393,604146}Concentrate and be cheerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.14,0:10:06.56,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:604146,606565}Ayumi is Midori…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:09.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606565,609193}Sakurakōji is Shinyo…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.19,0:10:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609193,611946}I wonder if we can beat Ondine…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.94,0:10:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:611946,616200}We have no choice but to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.20,0:10:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:616200,617868}Our reputation is at stake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.86,0:10:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:617868,619036}That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619036,621914}Our theatre might go out of business.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.91,0:10:23.99,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:621914,623998}Our theater might go out of business…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.99,0:10:25.70,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:623998,625709}Our theater will go out of business…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:627628,630089}Please, please! Choose whatever you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.08,0:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:630089,632424}I will take care of the bill.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.67,0:10:35.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:633676,635219}Wow, that's why I like you, Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.21,0:10:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635219,636595}Hey, let's have a tea party.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.59,0:10:39.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:636595,639223}We'll reserve a restaurant on the hill\Nso everyone can see us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.22,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:639223,641142}What about the Gentō?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.72,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:643727,646689}She knows precisely how to play this role.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.68,0:10:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:646689,651152}Other theaters chickened out after they heard\Nwe chose Himekawa Ayumi for the main role.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.98,0:10:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:651986,654989}Tsukigake Theatre will be hardly a threat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:657449,658784}Oh yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.78,0:11:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:658784,661035}I heard the girl\Nthat played Beth in "Little Women"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.03,0:11:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:661035,664123}was picked by Tsukikage Theatre to play Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.12,0:11:05.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:664123,665082}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.08,0:11:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665082,667543}Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.54,0:11:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:667543,669962}With such little acting experience…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.96,0:11:14.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:669962,674049}Isn't it a bit harsh of them\Nto match her up against Ayumi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.17,0:11:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:677178,678554}Is that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.84,0:11:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:679847,681849}The girl that played Beth…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.81,0:11:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:685811,687855}If you want to fight Shōta,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.85,0:11:30.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:687855,690481}then fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.44,0:11:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:691442,693569}Maya, get more upset!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.56,0:11:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:693569,694695}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.69,0:11:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:694695,695988}Shōta, we'll kick your ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696447,698449}Wait, wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.44,0:11:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:698449,700284}You don't have any guts, San Chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700284,703787}If you want to fight Shōta, then fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.70,0:11:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:704705,706165}Tremble your lips.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.16,0:11:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:706165,707416}Tremble your voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.41,0:11:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:707416,709293}Move your arms more!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.29,0:11:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709293,711545}Uh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.54,0:11:54.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:711545,714131}He won't run or hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.13,0:11:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:714131,716759}Look at where Shōta is!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.75,0:11:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:716759,718093}Stop, Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.09,0:12:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:718093,720054}Ah! Let me go, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.05,0:12:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720054,721580}You are so spiteful, Chokichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.58,0:12:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:721580,724642}If you want to fight him,\Nhit me. Go through me first!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.56,0:12:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:726560,727353}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.35,0:12:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:727353,731774}Midori has become so angry\Nshe can't control herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.77,0:12:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:731774,733150}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.15,0:12:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:733150,734151}San Chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.15,0:12:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:734151,735444}You don't have any guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.44,0:12:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:735444,737154}If you want to fight Shōta—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.99,0:12:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:740991,741909}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.28,0:12:25.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:743285,745285}San Chan, you don't have any guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:26.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745285,746497}If you want—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.62,0:12:31.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:748624,751335}S… San Chan, you don't have any g—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.58,0:12:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:753587,755047}S… San Chan—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.54,0:12:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:755547,756465}Maya…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.84,0:12:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756840,758133}San Chan…!
Comment: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:55.77,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:775775,775775}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:12:59.77,0:12:59.77,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:779779,779779}#Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:02.78,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:782782,782782}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.03,0:13:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:785034,786035}Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786035,787162}Do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.12,0:13:11.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:789123,791208}Did you hear me, Maya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.33,0:13:14.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:793335,794753}I said, do it again!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.22,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:812229,813564}Sa… San Chan…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.64,0:13:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815649,818152}you don't have any guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.69,0:13:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:819695,823991}If you want to fight Shōta, then fight him!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.99,0:13:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:823991,826869}He won't run or hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.86,0:13:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:826869,830789}Look at where Shōta is!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.78,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:830789,832041}Lady from Fude.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.04,0:13:54.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832041,834335}Ah… Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.33,0:13:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834335,835711}Stop, Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.71,0:13:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:835711,836879}Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.87,0:13:59.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:836879,839882}Ah! Let me go, Auntie!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.88,0:14:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:839882,844053}You are so spiteful, Chokichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844053,846219}If you want to fight him, hit me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.30,0:14:10.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:849308,850350}Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.14,0:14:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:852144,854480}Well done.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.48,0:14:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:854480,856231}Let's move on to the next scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.23,0:14:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:856231,857440}– Chokichi!\N– Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.82,0:14:30.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868826,870371}Teacher.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.37,0:14:33.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:870371,873248}When you began to hit me,\NI almost started to hate you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.24,0:14:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:873248,875876}Why did you keep doing that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.87,0:14:40.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:875876,880130}But then, that hate came out\Nthrough my body and my voice,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.13,0:14:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880130,883300}and I wasn't myself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.30,0:14:47.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:883300,887429}And now I know how to act…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.39,0:14:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:890391,892100}I don't know who or where you are,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:892100,894269}but you are my only fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.26,0:14:56.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:894269,896939}Mr. Purple Rose.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:896939,899400}For you, I'll try my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.38,0:15:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:922381,923840}Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.51,0:15:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:935519,937229}May I offer you my assistance?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.22,0:15:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:937229,938188}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941567,942651}Ah, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.65,0:15:43.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:942651,943861}How's my father?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:943861,945028}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.02,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:945028,946613}He is in his room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:946613,950868}He would like to hear\Nabout how your business went today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.86,0:15:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:950868,952953}Okay, I'll be there in a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.95,0:15:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:952953,954746}I will inform him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.45,0:15:58.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:957458,958917}Today's business, huh…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.00,0:16:02.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:961003,962504}Business, business…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.38,0:16:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:966383,969761}We only continue to be father and son\Nbecause of the business we share.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.76,0:16:13.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:969761,973931}Ever since my father became\Nthe president of Metropolitan Entertainment,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.93,0:16:17.22,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973931,977227}I was raised to live for his company
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.22,0:16:18.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:977227,978937}and I thought it was okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.93,0:16:22.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:978937,982190}I didn't know any other way to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.48,0:16:23.73,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:982483,983734}Masumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.73,0:16:26.57,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:983734,986570}Do as your father says.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.57,0:16:30.90,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:986570,990907}You will live for the Hayami family\Nand for your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.90,0:16:37.37,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:990907,997372}Never forget that, you are meant to help your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.37,0:16:41.29,Retrospective,,0,0,0,,{TIME:997372,1001292}Then he will take care of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.37,0:16:46.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1004379,1006882}But why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.88,0:16:50.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1006882,1010135}Why do I now rebel against it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.13,0:16:56.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1010135,1016391}I want to cast off this life\Nand be poor and free,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.39,0:16:57.80,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1016391,1017809}just like that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.06,0:17:05.39,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022064,1025399}I wish I had the strength\Nto choose the life I live,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.32,0:17:09.94,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1028320,1029946}just like she's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.94,0:17:12.65,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1029946,1032657}As the opening date\Nfor the Acting Contest came closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.65,0:17:15.57,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1032657,1035577}Tsukikage Theatre prepared for their rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.57,0:17:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1035577,1039665}Afternoon rehearsals starts at 1 PM tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1039665,1043335}This is Tsukikage Theatre.\NWe have our rehearsal scheduled for 6:30 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.33,0:17:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1043335,1044878}6:30 PM?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.87,0:17:29.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1044878,1049091}Actually a sound check is scheduled\Nto be conducted starting at 4 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.09,0:17:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1049091,1051677}Are you sure there's no mistake?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1051677,1052718}No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.71,0:17:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052718,1054471}We confirmed it with the Association.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.47,0:17:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054471,1056098}Oh, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1056098,1058600}They must have forgotten to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.60,0:17:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1058600,1061603}Since the sound check was scheduled for today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.60,0:17:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1061603,1064773}your rehearsal was changed to last Wednesday.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.10,0:17:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066108,1067275}Here, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.27,0:17:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1067275,1068694}That's ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.69,0:17:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1068694,1071446}Okay, if not today, when will we rehearse?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.44,0:17:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1071446,1072531}You're out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.53,0:17:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1072531,1076368}Today is the last day\Nfor district audition rehearsals.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.36,0:17:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1076368,1077995}– Last day?\N– No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.99,0:18:01.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1077995,1081498}Are you expecting us\Nto go on stage without rehearsing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1081498,1086753}Without being familiar with\Nthe stage entrances or lighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086753,1087754}This is absurd!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:11.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1087754,1091258}Well, I can't do anything about it…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.25,0:18:13.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1091258,1093510}Hey, Ondine is rehearsing!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.51,0:18:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1093510,1094720}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1094720,1096054}Ondine Theatre?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.05,0:18:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1096054,1097514}Let's go see, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.51,0:18:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1097514,1098390}Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.47,0:18:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1099474,1101518}Ah, right! Miss Tsukikage.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.51,0:18:25.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1101518,1105230}Go talk to Mr. Onodera of Ondine Theatre.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.23,0:18:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1105230,1107941}He did the scheduling.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.94,0:18:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1107941,1108900}Onodera?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.36,0:18:38.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1117367,1118577}Mr. Nobu…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.16,0:18:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1120162,1122205}Clean off the mud with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.33,0:18:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1124333,1125626}Uh, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1129880,1133091}He happily said "thank you" to the woman,\Neven though he's a monk.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.09,0:18:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1133091,1135802}I wonder if Midori will become Nobu's wife…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.80,0:18:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1135802,1138889}He's not good enough for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.88,0:19:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1138889,1141725}Be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.72,0:19:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1141725,1142893}Mr. Nobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.89,0:19:03.93,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142893,1143935}It's different.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.93,0:19:06.68,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1143935,1146688}She's so different from my Midori…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.68,0:19:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1146688,1147688}Mr. Nobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150192,1152861}He's never so rude to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.86,0:19:14.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1152861,1154529}But he's always like that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.73,0:19:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1155739,1158742}He never responds when I talk to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.74,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1158742,1160744}and he runs when I get near.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.99,0:19:27.83,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1163997,1167834}Every one of her movements are glowing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.83,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1167834,1169127}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.17,0:19:36.13,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1174174,1176134}Her movements…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.01,0:19:39.76,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178011,1179763}Her face…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.76,0:19:40.88,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1179763,1180889}Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.88,0:19:43.55,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1180889,1183558}In every way, she's the real Midori!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.36,0:19:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1195362,1197447}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.44,0:20:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1197447,1200075}Why is he so cold?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1200075,1201447}Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.82,0:20:38.53,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1236820,1238530}It's hopeless…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.53,0:20:40.40,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1238530,1240407}There's no way I can win.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.57,0:20:46.12,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1243577,1246121}It's true, she's a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.12,0:20:49.70,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1246121,1249707}My acting can't even compare to hers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.70,0:20:50.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1249707,1250834}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1250834,1252711}What's wrong? Practice starts soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:53.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1252711,1253544}Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.54,0:20:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1253544,1254545}I'm not coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.54,0:20:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1254545,1255130}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.84,0:20:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1256840,1259134}I can't do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.13,0:21:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1259134,1261553}There's no way I can act better than Ayumi—
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.55,0:21:03.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1261553,1263221}What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.22,0:21:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1263221,1267476}No one can play Midori\Nbetter than you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.47,0:21:08.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1267476,1268518}Here, come on, Maya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.51,0:21:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1268518,1269853}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1271438,1274483}I can't! I just can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.48,0:21:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1274483,1277944}When I say Midori's words,\Nor do her movements,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.94,0:21:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1277944,1280947}I can only think of Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.94,0:21:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1280947,1281656}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.65,0:21:23.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1281656,1283241}It's useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:26.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1286036,1286995}Maya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.62,0:21:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1289623,1292208}Do you intend to surrender\Nbefore the battle has begun?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.08,0:21:37.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1294085,1297547}Teacher, there's such a big difference\Nbetween me and Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.54,0:21:40.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1297547,1300675}I realized it at that rehearsal.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.67,0:21:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1300675,1303929}I can't play Midori.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.92,0:21:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1303929,1306848}Maya, is this really who you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.84,0:21:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1306848,1310602}Are you the kind of girl who would run\Nin the face of a little struggle?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:53.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1310602,1313939}I was unaware that you were so weak.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.93,0:21:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1313939,1318485}Himekawa Ayumi is not defeating you,\Nyou are losing to yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1319611,1322656}I'm sorry, I can't play Midori anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.65,0:22:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1322656,1324241}I can't continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.24,0:22:04.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324241,1324991}I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.99,0:22:06.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1324991,1326659}That's too bad, but fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.65,0:22:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1326659,1329162}You will be relieved of your role.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.16,0:22:11.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1329162,1331039}Now, come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.03,0:22:12.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1331039,1332958}Teacher, let me go, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.95,0:22:15.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1332958,1335585}Everyone has tried so hard,\Nbut you dare to give up?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1337754,1340841}Don't even try to attend practice\Nuntil the district contest is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1340841,1342926}Until then, think about what you have done!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.84,0:22:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1348849,1350600}I can't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1350600,1353645}I can't act as good as Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.64,0:22:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1353645,1355689}There's just…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.68,0:22:38.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1355689,1358817}There's too much difference between us!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.81,0:22:41.19,Thought,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1358817,1361194}There's too much difference between us!
Comment: 0,0:22:50.87,0:22:50.87,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1370870,1370870}Ending
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.25,0:23:04.38,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1378252,1384383}{\blur3}It is lonely by myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.38,0:23:10.47,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1384383,1390472}{\blur3}and I almost stumble.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.47,0:23:22.48,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1390472,1402484}{\blur3}Something calls me here,\Njust like a whisper in the wind.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.48,0:23:34.62,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1402484,1414622}{\blur3}Purple light, shining down\Non the horizon,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.62,0:23:40.46,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1414622,1420461}{\blur3}more surer than words,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.46,0:23:46.63,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1420461,1426634}{\blur3}telling us gently
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.63,0:23:52.72,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1426634,1432723}{\blur3}that we'll meet\Neach other someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.72,0:23:58.77,Ending alt,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:1432723,1438771}{\blur3}Of course you can\Nfly from far away,
