Comment: 0,0:24:20.96,0:24:20.96,Default,[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:1460960,1460960}Preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.33,0:24:25.67,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1463337,1465673}Ayumi's performance as Midori is completely perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.67,0:24:29.05,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1465673,1469051}Maya is overwhelmed and loses her confidence.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.05,0:24:36.30,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1469051,1476308}However, as a result of special training,\NMaya finds a Midori that contrasts with Ayumi's.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.30,0:24:39.97,Narrator,(narrator),0,0,0,,{TIME:1476308,1479979}Please look forward to the next episode:\N"Two Midoris".
